I cant believe no one has commented on this...

This is an RMVB file so unless you want to spend hours converting this to a format everyone else in the world uses dont download or use this program to convert...

http://thepiratebay.org/tor/3705425/Magic_Video_Converter_8.0.2.18_(The_Ultimate_Video_Converter)
I just renamed it to .avi and it played fine.  I have the klite codec set installed, so I'm sure something in there picked it up.
